Stallone for three months.

02:48.350 --> 02:50.286
I got a Corvette.

02:51.754 --> 02:53.423
Let me see the 'Vette.

02:56.624 --> 03:00.993
<i>And there he was, my old classmate.</i>

03:00.995 --> 03:03.296
<i>He hadn't changed a bit.</i>

03:03.298 --> 03:04.664
If we take the over and the under...

03:04.666 --> 03:08.367
<i>He was still the
smartest guy in the room.</i>

03:08.369 --> 03:10.772
<i>Still wearing the cheapest suit.</i>

03:13.374 --> 03:15.342
Sorry, ahh...

03:15.344 --> 03:16.475
Corvette.

03:16.477 --> 03:18.280
Mr. Ioku... thank you.

03:19.781 --> 03:22.415
- Dean.
- Joe.

03:22.417 --> 03:24.418
- It's been forever.
- Way too long.

03:24.420 --> 03:26.086
Come here, man.

03:26.088 --> 03:30.356
So, making moves, what have you been up to?

03:30.358 --> 03:32.325
I am working at the Pacific Stock Exchange.

03:32.327 --> 03:34.694
Wall Street of the West, nice.

03:34.696 --> 03:36.096
And what are you up to?

03:36.098 --> 03:40.099
A bit of this, a bit of that.

03:40.101 --> 03:42.336
Are you living downtown?

03:42.338 --> 03:43.969
I'm still living with my father.

03:43.971 --> 03:45.338
Are you shitting me?

03:45.340 --> 03:46.907
Are they not paying you?

03:46.909 --> 03:48.444
Barely.

03:52.681 --> 03:54.848
Is that cash?

03:54.850 --> 03:57.516
Yeah, I just sold the Biltmores a Corvette.

03:57.518 --> 03:59.652
Joe, you shouldn't be
working for these guys.

03:59.654 --> 04:02.122
You should be these guys.
You've gotta get your own thing.

04:02.124 --> 04:05.425
Thanks, I appreciate it.

04:05.427 --> 04:10.497
