money, and things I don't have.

04:10.499 --> 04:12.435
You know, we would make the perfect team.

04:14.535 --> 04:16.702
Come to Spago tonight. It's
Charlie Bottom's birthday.

04:16.704 --> 04:18.372
We could go talk to him.

04:18.374 --> 04:19.572
Charlie Bottoms from high school?

04:19.574 --> 04:20.807
Yeah.

04:20.809 --> 04:21.908
