06:08.617 --> 06:10.115
Come on, Mr. T, may we?

06:10.117 --> 06:12.052
- You got it.
- Thank you.

06:12.054 --> 06:13.823
- Thank you.
- See you later.

06:21.730 --> 06:24.163
Dude, what happened to
us both being Reagan?

06:24.165 --> 06:30.005
