work for Barbara Walters.

15:03.450 --> 15:05.451
Tell 'em you are Barbara
Walters if you have to.

15:05.453 --> 15:07.787
This press badge will get you
access everywhere, all right?

15:07.789 --> 15:10.756
Listen to me, front row. That
close up of John DeLorean?

15:10.758 --> 15:12.792
