it! Do you understand?

15:12.794 --> 15:15.028
Yes, sir.

15:15.030 --> 15:16.562
Ah yes.

15:16.564 --> 15:20.099
Bon jour, combien allez-vous
payer des photo de Jon Delorean?

15:21.636 --> 15:24.669
Ah oui, merci.

15:24.671 --> 15:26.538
Nigel, we're a go.

15:26.540 --> 15:30.275
Yes. Buy GM the moment that
those charges are announced.

15:30.277 --> 15:35.048
Yes, at 52 and a half.
That's right, thank you.

15:35.050 --> 15:37.149
<i>Ron Levin was a force of nature.</i>

15:37.151 --> 15:38.784
Oh, hi, Giselle. Hi, it's Ronnie.

15:38.786 --> 15:40.720
Yeah, I'd like three chopped salads.

15:40.722 --> 15:41.955
<i>Made a fortune on Wall Street...</i>

15:41.957 --> 15:44.157
<i>with the Rothschild Group
before going west...</i>

15:44.159 --> 15:47.225
