01:23:46.736 --> 01:23:49.505
No, no, this thing is over.

01:23:49.507 --> 01:23:51.843
Come on.

01:23:53.511 --> 01:23:55.280
Look, guys.

01:23:57.280 --> 01:23:58.515
Oh, fuck.

01:24:55.672 --> 01:24:57.608
Sam?

01:25:02.846 --> 01:25:04.947
